@startuml
start

:MDM, channel, email, messaging, or file processing operation fails;
:Create or update Integration_Error__c with transaction ID and Case reference;
:Classify failure;

if (Retryable?) then (Yes)
  if (Retry count below limit?) then (Yes)
    :Increment retry count;
    :Queue retry using scheduled/batch/queueable process;
    :Keep Case in Verification Pending or Manual Review as needed;
  else (No)
    :Mark error as Max Retry Exceeded;
    :Notify Supervisor or Support Team;
  endif
else (No)
  :Mark error as Non-Retryable;
  :Notify responsible team;
endif

if (Retry succeeds?) then (Yes)
  :Update Case, Contact, and Integration Error status;
else (No)
  :Keep operational error visible on dashboard;
endif

stop
@enduml
